var book = {
	"name": "Song of Solomon",
	"numChapters": 8,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The Song of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17539A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17539A\"></sup>Songs, which is Solomon’s.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“May he kiss me with the kisses of his mouth!For your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17540B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17540B\"></sup>love is better than wine.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17541C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17541C\"></sup>oils have a pleasing fragrance,Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17541D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17541D\"></sup>name is <i>like</i> purified oil;Therefore the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17541E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17541E\"></sup>maidens love you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Draw me after you <i>and</i> let us run <i>together</i>!The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17542F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17542F\"></sup>king has brought me into his chambers.”“We will rejoice in you and be glad;We will extol your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17542G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17542G\"></sup>love more than wine.Rightly do they love you.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I am black but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17543H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17543H\"></sup>lovely,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17543I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17543I\"></sup>daughters of Jerusalem,Like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17543J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17543J\"></sup>tents of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17543K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17543K\"></sup>Kedar,Like the curtains of Solomon.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Do not stare at me because I am swarthy,For the sun has burned me.My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17544L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17544L\"></sup>mother’s sons were angry with me;They made me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17544M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17544M\"></sup>caretaker of the vineyards,<i>But</i> I have not taken care of my own vineyard.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Tell me, O you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17545N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17545N\"></sup>whom my soul loves,Where do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17545O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17545O\"></sup>pasture <i>your flock</i>,Where do you make <i>it</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17545P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17545P\"></sup>lie down at noon?For why should I be like one who veils herselfBeside the flocks of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17545Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17545Q\"></sup>companions?”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“If you yourself do not know,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17546R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17546R\"></sup>Most beautiful among women,Go forth on the trail of the flockAnd pasture your young goatsBy the tents of the shepherds.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“To me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17547S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17547S\"></sup>my darling, you are likeMy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17547T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17547T\"></sup>mare among the chariots of Pharaoh.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17548U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17548U\"></sup>cheeks are lovely with ornaments,Your neck with strings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17548V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17548V\"></sup>beads.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“We will make for you ornaments of goldWith beads of silver.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“While the king was at his table,My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17550W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17550W\"></sup>perfume gave forth its fragrance.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“My beloved is to me a pouch of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17551X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17551X\"></sup>myrrhWhich lies all night between my breasts.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“My beloved is to me a cluster of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17552Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17552Y\"></sup>henna blossomsIn the vineyards of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17552Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17552Z\"></sup>Engedi.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17553AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17553AA\"></sup>How beautiful you are, my darling,How beautiful you are!Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17553AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17553AB\"></sup>eyes are <i>like</i> doves.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“How handsome you are, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17554AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17554AC\"></sup>my beloved,<i>And</i> so pleasant!Indeed, our couch is luxuriant!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“The beams of our houses are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17555AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17555AD\"></sup>cedars,Our rafters, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17555AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17555AE\"></sup>cypresses."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>“I am the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17556A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17556A\"></sup>rose of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17556B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17556B\"></sup>Sharon,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17556C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17556C\"></sup>lily of the valleys.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Like a lily among the thorns,So is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17557D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17557D\"></sup>my darling among the maidens.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Like an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17558E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17558E\"></sup>apple tree among the trees of the forest,So is my beloved among the young men.In his shade I took great delight and sat down,And his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17558F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17558F\"></sup>fruit was sweet to my taste.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17559G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17559G\"></sup>brought me to <i>his</i> banquet hall,And his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17559H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17559H\"></sup>banner over me is love.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Sustain me with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17560I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17560I\"></sup>raisin cakes,Refresh me with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17560J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17560J\"></sup>apples,Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17560K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17560K\"></sup>I am lovesick.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17561L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17561L\"></sup>his left hand be under my headAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17561M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17561M\"></sup>his right hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17561N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17561N\"></sup>embrace me.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17562O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17562O\"></sup>adjure you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17562P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17562P\"></sup>daughters of Jerusalem,By the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17562Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17562Q\"></sup>gazelles or by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17562R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17562R\"></sup>hinds of the field,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17562S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17562S\"></sup>That you do not arouse or awaken <i>my</i> loveUntil she pleases.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Listen! My beloved!Behold, he is coming,Climbing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17563T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17563T\"></sup>on the mountains,Leaping on the hills!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“My beloved is like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17564U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17564U\"></sup>gazelle or a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17564V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17564V\"></sup>young stag.Behold, he is standing behind our wall,He is looking through the windows,He is peering <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17564W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17564W\"></sup>through the lattice.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“My beloved responded and said to me,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17565X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17565X\"></sup>Arise, my darling, my beautiful one,And come along.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>‘For behold, the winter is past,The rain is over <i>and</i> gone.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>‘The flowers have <i>already</i> appeared in the land;The time has arrived for pruning <i>the vines</i>,And the voice of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17567Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17567Y\"></sup>turtledove has been heard in our land.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17568Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17568Z\"></sup>fig tree has ripened its figs,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17568AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17568AA\"></sup>vines in blossom have given forth <i>their</i> fragrance.Arise, my darling, my beautiful one,And come along!’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17569AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17569AB\"></sup>my dove, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17569AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17569AC\"></sup>in the clefts of the rock,In the secret place of the steep pathway,Let me see your form,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17569AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17569AD\"></sup>Let me hear your voice;For your voice is sweet,And your form is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17569AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17569AE\"></sup>lovely.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17570AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17570AF\"></sup>Catch the foxes for us,The little foxes that are ruining the vineyards,While our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17570AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17570AG\"></sup>vineyards are in blossom.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17571AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17571AH\"></sup>My beloved is mine, and I am his;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17571AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17571AI\"></sup>pastures <i>his flock</i> among the lilies.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17572AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17572AJ\"></sup>Until the cool of the day when the shadows flee away,Turn, my beloved, and be like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17572AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17572AK\"></sup>gazelleOr a young stag <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17572AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17572AL\"></sup>on the mountains of Bether.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>“On my bed night after night I sought him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17573A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17573A\"></sup>Whom my soul loves;I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17573B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17573B\"></sup>sought him but did not find him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>‘I must arise now and go about the city;In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17574C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17574C\"></sup>streets and in the squaresI must seek him whom my soul loves.’I sought him but did not find him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17575D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17575D\"></sup>The watchmen who make the rounds in the city found me,<i>And I said</i>, ‘Have you seen him whom my soul loves?’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17576E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17576E\"></sup>Scarcely had I left themWhen I found him whom my soul loves;I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17576F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17576F\"></sup>held on to him and would not let him goUntil I had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17576G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17576G\"></sup>brought him to my mother’s house,And into the room of her who conceived me.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17577H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17577H\"></sup>adjure you, O daughters of Jerusalem,By the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17577I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17577I\"></sup>gazelles or by the hinds of the field,That you will not arouse or awaken <i>my</i> loveUntil she pleases.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17578J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17578J\"></sup>What is this coming up from the wildernessLike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17578K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17578K\"></sup>columns of smoke,Perfumed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17578L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17578L\"></sup>myrrh and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17578M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17578M\"></sup>frankincense,With all scented powders of the merchant?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Behold, it is the <i>traveling</i> couch of Solomon;Sixty mighty men around it,Of the mighty men of Israel.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“All of them are wielders of the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17580N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17580N\"></sup>Expert in war;Each man has his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17580O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17580O\"></sup>sword at his side,<i>Guarding</i> against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17580P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17580P\"></sup>terrors of the night.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“King Solomon has made for himself a sedan chairFrom the timber of Lebanon.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“He made its posts of silver,Its back of gold<i>And</i> its seat of purple fabric,<i>With</i> its interior lovingly fitted outBy the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17582Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17582Q\"></sup>daughters of Jerusalem.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Go forth, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17583R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17583R\"></sup>daughters of Zion,And gaze on King Solomon with the crownWith which his mother has crowned himOn the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17583S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17583S\"></sup>day of his wedding,And on the day of his gladness of heart.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>“How beautiful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17584A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17584A\"></sup>you are, my darling,How beautiful you are!Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17584B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17584B\"></sup>eyes are <i>like</i> doves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17584C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17584C\"></sup>behind your veil;Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17584D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17584D\"></sup>hair is like a flock of goatsThat have descended from Mount <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17584E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17584E\"></sup>Gilead.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17585F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17585F\"></sup>teeth are like a flock of <i>newly</i> shorn ewesWhich have come up from <i>their</i> washing,All of which bear twins,And not one among them has lost her young.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Your lips are like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17586G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17586G\"></sup>scarlet thread,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17586H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17586H\"></sup>mouth is lovely.Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17586I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17586I\"></sup>temples are like a slice of a pomegranateBehind your veil.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17587J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17587J\"></sup>neck is like the tower of David,Built with rows of stonesOn which are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17587K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17587K\"></sup>hung a thousand shields,All the round <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17587L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17587L\"></sup>shields of the mighty men.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17588M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17588M\"></sup>two breasts are like two fawns,Twins of a gazelleWhich <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17588N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17588N\"></sup>feed among the lilies.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17589O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17589O\"></sup>Until the cool of the dayWhen the shadows flee away,I will go my way to the mountain of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17589P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17589P\"></sup>myrrhAnd to the hill of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17589Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17589Q\"></sup>frankincense.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17590R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17590R\"></sup>You are altogether beautiful, my darling,And there is no blemish in you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<i>Come</i> with me from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17591S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17591S\"></sup>Lebanon, <i>my</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17591T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17591T\"></sup>bride,May you come with me from Lebanon.Journey down from the summit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17591U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17591U\"></sup>Amana,From the summit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17591V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17591V\"></sup>Senir and Hermon,From the dens of lions,From the mountains of leopards.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“You have made my heart beat faster, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17592W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17592W\"></sup>my sister, <i>my</i> bride;You have made my heart beat faster with a single <i>glance</i> of your eyes,With a single strand of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17592X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17592X\"></sup>necklace.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17593Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17593Y\"></sup>How beautiful is your love, my sister, <i>my</i> bride!How much <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17593Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17593Z\"></sup>better is your love than wine,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17593AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17593AA\"></sup>fragrance of your oilsThan all <i>kinds</i> of spices!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Your lips, <i>my</i> bride, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17594AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17594AB\"></sup>drip <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17594AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17594AC\"></sup>honey;Honey and milk are under your tongue,And the fragrance of your garments is like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17594AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17594AD\"></sup>fragrance of Lebanon.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“A garden locked is my sister, <i>my</i> bride,A rock garden locked, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17595AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17595AE\"></sup>spring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17595AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17595AF\"></sup>sealed up.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Your shoots are an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17596AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17596AG\"></sup>orchard of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17596AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17596AH\"></sup>pomegranatesWith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17596AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17596AI\"></sup>choice fruits, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17596AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17596AJ\"></sup>henna with nard plants,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17597AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17597AK\"></sup>Nard and saffron, calamus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17597AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17597AL\"></sup>cinnamon,With all the trees of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17597AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17597AM\"></sup>frankincense,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17597AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17597AN\"></sup>Myrrh and aloes, along with all the finest spices.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<i>You are</i> a garden spring,A well of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17598AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17598AO\"></sup>fresh water,And streams <i>flowing</i> from Lebanon.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Awake, O north <i>wind</i>,And come, <i>wind of</i> the south;Make my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17599AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17599AP\"></sup>garden breathe out <i>fragrance</i>,Let its spices be wafted abroad.May <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17599AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17599AQ\"></sup>my beloved come into his gardenAnd eat its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17599AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17599AR\"></sup>choice fruits!”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>“I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17600A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17600A\"></sup>come into my garden, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17600B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17600B\"></sup>my sister, <i>my</i> bride;I have gathered my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17600C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17600C\"></sup>myrrh along with my balsam.I have eaten my honeycomb and my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17600D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17600D\"></sup>honey;I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17600E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17600E\"></sup>drunk my wine and my milk.Eat, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17600F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17600F\"></sup>friends;Drink and imbibe deeply, O lovers.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I was asleep but my heart was awake.A voice! My beloved was knocking:‘Open to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17601G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17601G\"></sup>my sister, my darling,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17601H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17601H\"></sup>My dove, my perfect one!For my head is drenched with dew,My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17601I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17601I\"></sup>locks with the damp of the night.’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17602J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17602J\"></sup>taken off my dress,How can I put it on <i>again</i>?I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17602K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17602K\"></sup>washed my feet,How can I dirty them <i>again</i>?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“My beloved extended his hand through the opening,And my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17603L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17603L\"></sup>feelings were aroused for him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I arose to open to my beloved;And my hands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17604M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17604M\"></sup>dripped with myrrh,And my fingers with liquid myrrh,On the handles of the bolt.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I opened to my beloved,But my beloved had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17605N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17605N\"></sup>turned away <i>and</i> had gone!My heart went out <i>to him</i> as he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17605O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17605O\"></sup>spoke.I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17605P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17605P\"></sup>searched for him but I did not find him;I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17605Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17605Q\"></sup>called him but he did not answer me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17606R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17606R\"></sup>watchmen who make the rounds in the city found me,They struck me <i>and</i> wounded me;The guardsmen of the walls took away my shawl from me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17607S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17607S\"></sup>adjure you, O daughters of Jerusalem,If you find my beloved,As to what you will tell him:For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17607T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17607T\"></sup>I am lovesick.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“What kind of beloved is your beloved,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17608U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17608U\"></sup>most beautiful among women?What kind of beloved is your beloved,That thus you adjure us?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“My beloved is dazzling and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17609V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17609V\"></sup>ruddy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17609W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17609W\"></sup>Outstanding among ten thousand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“His head is <i>like</i> gold, pure gold;His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17610X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17610X\"></sup>locks are <i>like</i> clusters of dates<i>And</i> black as a raven.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17611Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17611Y\"></sup>eyes are like dovesBeside streams of water,Bathed in milk,<i>And</i> reposed in <i>their</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17611Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17611Z\"></sup>setting.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“His cheeks are like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17612AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17612AA\"></sup>bed of balsam,Banks of sweet-scented herbs;His lips are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17612AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17612AB\"></sup>lilies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17612AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17612AC\"></sup>Dripping with liquid myrrh.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“His hands are rods of goldSet with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17613AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17613AD\"></sup>beryl;His abdomen is carved ivoryInlaid with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17613AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17613AE\"></sup>sapphires.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“His legs are pillars of alabasterSet on pedestals of pure gold;His appearance is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17614AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17614AF\"></sup>LebanonChoice as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17614AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17614AG\"></sup>cedars.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17615AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17615AH\"></sup>mouth is <i>full of</i> sweetness.And he is wholly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17615AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17615AI\"></sup>desirable.This is my beloved and this is my friend,O daughters of Jerusalem.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17616A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17616A\"></sup>Where has your beloved gone,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17616B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17616B\"></sup>most beautiful among women?Where has your beloved turned,That we may seek him with you?”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“My beloved has gone down to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17617C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17617C\"></sup>garden,To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17617D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17617D\"></sup>beds of balsam,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17617E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17617E\"></sup>pasture <i>his flock</i> in the gardensAnd gather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17617F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17617F\"></sup>lilies.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17618G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17618G\"></sup>I am my beloved’s and my beloved is mine,He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17618H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17618H\"></sup>pastures <i>his flock</i> among the lilies.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17619I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17619I\"></sup>You are as beautiful as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17619J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17619J\"></sup>Tirzah, my darling,As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17619K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17619K\"></sup>lovely as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17619L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17619L\"></sup>Jerusalem,As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17619M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17619M\"></sup>awesome as an army with banners.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Turn your eyes away from me,For they have confused me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17620N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17620N\"></sup>Your hair is like a flock of goatsThat have descended from Gilead.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17621O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17621O\"></sup>Your teeth are like a flock of ewesWhich have come up from <i>their</i> washing,All of which bear twins,And not one among them has lost her young.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17622P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17622P\"></sup>Your temples are like a slice of a pomegranateBehind your veil.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“There are sixty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17623Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17623Q\"></sup>queens and eighty concubines,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17623R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17623R\"></sup>maidens without number;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><i>But</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17624S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17624S\"></sup>my dove, my perfect one, is unique:She is her mother’s only <i>daughter</i>;She is the pure <i>child</i> of the one who bore her.The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17624T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17624T\"></sup>maidens saw her and called her blessed,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17624U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17624U\"></sup>queens and the concubines <i>also</i>, and they praised her, <i>saying</i>,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Who is this that grows like the dawn,As beautiful as the full <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17625V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17625V\"></sup>moon,As pure <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17625W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17625W\"></sup>as the sun,As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17625X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17625X\"></sup>awesome as an army with banners?’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I went down to the orchard of nut treesTo see the blossoms of the valley,To see whether <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17626Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17626Y\"></sup>the vine had budded<i>Or</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17626Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17626Z\"></sup>pomegranates had bloomed.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Before I was aware, my soul set me<i>Over</i> the chariots of my noble people.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Come back, come back, O Shulammite;Come back, come back, that we may gaze at you!”“Why should you gaze at the Shulammite,As at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17628AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17628AA\"></sup>dance of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17628AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17628AB\"></sup>the two companies?"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>“How beautiful are your feet in sandals,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17629A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17629A\"></sup>prince’s daughter!The curves of your hips are like jewels,The work of the hands of an artist.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Your navel is <i>like</i> a round gobletWhich never lacks mixed wine;Your belly is like a heap of wheatFenced about with lilies.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17631B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17631B\"></sup>two breasts are like two fawns,Twins of a gazelle.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17632C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17632C\"></sup>neck is like a tower of ivory,Your eyes <i>like</i> the pools in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17632D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17632D\"></sup>HeshbonBy the gate of Bath-rabbim;Your nose is like the tower of Lebanon,Which faces toward Damascus.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Your head crowns you like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17633E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17633E\"></sup>Carmel,And the flowing locks of your head are like purple threads;<i>The</i> king is captivated by <i>your</i> tresses.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17634F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17634F\"></sup>beautiful and how delightful you are,<i>My</i> love, with <i>all</i> your charms!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Your stature is like a palm tree,And your breasts are <i>like its</i> clusters.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“I said, ‘I will climb the palm tree,I will take hold of its fruit stalks.’Oh, may your breasts be like clusters of the vine,And the fragrance of your breath like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17636G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17636G\"></sup>apples,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17637H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17637H\"></sup>mouth like the best wine!”“It <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17637I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17637I\"></sup>goes <i>down</i> smoothly for my beloved,Flowing gently <i>through</i> the lips of those who fall asleep.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17638J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17638J\"></sup>I am my beloved’s,And his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17638K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17638K\"></sup>desire is for me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Come, my beloved, let us go out into the country,Let us spend the night in the villages.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Let us rise early <i>and go</i> to the vineyards;Let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17640L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17640L\"></sup>see whether the vine has budded<i>And its</i> blossoms have opened,<i>And whether</i> the pomegranates have bloomed.There I will give you my love.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17641M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17641M\"></sup>mandrakes have given forth fragrance;And over our doors are all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17641N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17641N\"></sup>choice <i>fruits</i>,Both new and old,Which I have saved up for you, my beloved."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>“Oh that you were like a brother to meWho nursed at my mother’s breasts.<i>If</i> I found you outdoors, I would kiss you;No one would despise me, either.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I would lead you <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17643A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17643A\"></sup>bring youInto the house of my mother, who used to instruct me;I would give you spiced wine to drink from the juice of my pomegranates.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17644B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17644B\"></sup>his left hand be under my headAnd his right hand embrace me.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17645C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17645C\"></sup>I want you to swear, O daughters of Jerusalem,Do not arouse or awaken <i>my</i> loveUntil she pleases.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17646D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17646D\"></sup>Who is this coming up from the wildernessLeaning on her beloved?”“Beneath the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17646E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17646E\"></sup>apple tree I awakened you;There your mother was in labor with you,There she was in labor <i>and</i> gave you birth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Put me like a seal over your heart,Like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17647F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17647F\"></sup>seal on your arm.For love is as strong as death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17647G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17647G\"></sup>Jealousy is as severe as Sheol;Its flashes are flashes of fire,The <i>very</i> flame of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Many waters cannot quench love,Nor will rivers overflow it;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17648H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17648H\"></sup>If a man were to give all the riches of his house for love,It would be utterly despised.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“We have a little sister,And she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17649I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17649I\"></sup>has no breasts;What shall we do for our sisterOn the day when she is spoken for?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“If she is a wall,We will build on her a battlement of silver;But if she is a door,We will barricade her with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17650J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17650J\"></sup>planks of cedar.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“I was a wall, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17651K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17651K\"></sup>my breasts were like towers;Then I became in his eyes as one who finds peace.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Solomon had a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17652L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17652L\"></sup>vineyard at Baal-hamon;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17652M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17652M\"></sup>entrusted the vineyard to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17652N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17652N\"></sup>caretakers.Each one was to bring a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17652O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17652O\"></sup>thousand <i>shekels</i> of silver for its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17652P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17652P\"></sup>fruit.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“My very own vineyard is at my disposal;The thousand <i>shekels</i> are for you, Solomon,And two hundred are for those who take care of its fruit.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“O you who sit in the gardens,<i>My</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17654Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17654Q\"></sup>companions are listening for your voice—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17654R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17654R\"></sup>Let me hear it!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Hurry, my beloved,And be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17655S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17655S\"></sup>like a gazelle or a young stagOn the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17655T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17655T\"></sup>mountains of spices.”"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;